tr.td: Bistable regime, converging to either a coral death equilibrium with sustainable parrotfish density or the unassisted macroalgae-free equilibrium.
Behaviour stabilizes to either a limit cycle or the assisted macroalgae-free equilibrium.

Tristable regime, stabilizing to either: ( 1) a coral death equilibrium with parrotfish survival and full conservation cooperation, ( 2) a catastrophic equilibrium with parrotfish extinction with full conservation cooperation or ( 3) the assisted macroalgae-free equilibrium.
Bistable regime, stabilizing to either the assisted macroalgae-free equilibrium or a state of coral and macroalgal decimation, with human-assisted parrotfish survival.

Tristable regime, stabilizing to either: ( 1) the unassisted macroalgae-free equilibrium, ( 2) the assisted macroalgae-free equilibrium, or ( 3) a state governed by a human-unassisted coral death equilibrium, with sustainable parrotfish density.
Bistable regime, stabilizing to either the unassisted macroalgae-free equilibrium or a state governed by the human-unassisted coral death equilibrium, with sustainable parrotfish density.
Tristable regime, with behaviour converging to either behaviour of ( D), or a state governed by the human-unassisted coral death equilibrium, solely governed by macroalgae.
